# Homepage lock (approved 2026-06-03)

The Green Wing homepage visual polish is **complete and locked**. Do not change it unless the user **explicitly** asks to edit the homepage.

## Do not modify without explicit user request

- `index.html` — full homepage markup and copy
- Homepage-only sections in `css/styles.css` (hero video, logo marquee, trusted strip, problem/journey/services/proof/roadmap/sectors/FAQ/CTA homepage blocks, footer-slim, section dividers/motifs)
- Homepage init in `js/main.js` (`initVideoHero`, `initLogoMarquee`, footer render if it affects homepage)

## Allowed without unlocking

- Other site pages (`services.html`, `about.html`, etc.)
- Non-homepage CSS/JS (e.g. contact form, inner-page layouts)
- Bug fixes only if the user reports a homepage bug and asks for a fix

## If homepage changes are requested

Confirm scope with the user, make the smallest diff, and do not refactor unrelated homepage sections.
